sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as OpenShift Gateway<br/>(data-science-gateway)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pods<br/>6379/TCP TCP
    participant Operator as kuberay-operator<br/>(opendatahub ns)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Access to Ray Dashboard (Gateway API Pattern)

    User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Auth decision
    KRBP->>RayHead: Proxy to dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265 (localhost, plaintext)
    RayHead-->>KRBP: Dashboard response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response (TLS)
    Gateway-->>User: Response (TLS 1.2+)

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 2: RayCluster Lifecycle Management

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRDs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: RayCluster event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Worker Pods,<br/>Services, NetworkPolicies<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    Operator->>RayHead: Health check<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext

    Note over RayHead,CertMgr: Flow 2b: Intra-cluster Communication (with mTLS)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create cert-manager Issuer + Certificates
    CertMgr-->>K8sAPI: Provision TLS secrets
    RayHead->>RayWorker: GCS communication<br/>TCP/6379, mTLS (cert-manager)
    RayWorker->>RayHead: GCS communication<br/>TCP/6379, mTLS (cert-manager)

    Note over Operator,RayHead: Flow 3: RayJob Submission

    participant Submitter as Submitter Job Pod

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job resource<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job created
    Submitter->>RayHead: Submit Ray job<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext
    RayHead-->>Submitter: Job accepted
    Operator->>RayHead: Poll job status<br/>HTTP/8265, plaintext
    RayHead-->>Operator: Job status

    Note over K8sAPI,Operator: Flow 4: Webhook Admission

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Admission request<br/>HTTPS/443 -> 9443/TCP<br/>TLS (OpenShift serving cert)
    Operator-->>K8sAPI: Mutated/Validated response<br/>enableIngress=false<br/>secure-trusted-network=true
